## 12. IMAGE GENERATION PIPELINE

### Three-Layer Protection System
1. **AI Prompt Layer** (bot-chat): Explicit instructions to include Unsplash URLs
2. **Post-Processor Layer** (BuilderShell): imageFiller fills missing images after parsing
3. **Renderer Fallback** (SiteRenderer): Final check before display

### Industry-Specific Image Keywords
| Industry | Primary Keywords | Secondary Keywords |
|----------|-----------------|-------------------|
| Restaurant | food plating, restaurant interior | chef, dining, cuisine |
| Fitness | gym equipment, workout | trainer, exercise, health |
| Salon | hair styling, beauty | spa, treatment, wellness |
| Legal | law office, courthouse | documents, professional |
| Medical | healthcare, clinic | doctor, patient care |
| Real Estate | modern home, interior | architecture, property |
| Contractor | construction, tools | renovation, building |

### URL Format Standards
- Hero images: `?w=1600&h=900&fit=crop`
- Gallery items: `?w=800&h=600&fit=crop`
- Team avatars: `?w=200&h=200&fit=crop&facepad=2`
- Service cards: `?w=600&h=400&fit=crop`